    "Probation sentences and monetary nes are much more frequent but still apply in only about 10% of the cases each.",
    "Monetary nes are mostly very small relative to prison sentences.",
    "The median non-zero monetary ne is $2,000, and the 90th percentile is $15,000.",
    "We thus ignore them as well, and focus exclusively on prison sentences.",
    "Our identication strategy relies on a parallel trends assumption."
